      <title>本田接近与加拿大达成协议以提高电动汽车产能</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/honda-is-near-deal-with-canada-to-boost-electric-vehicle-capacity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，加拿大即将与本田汽车公司达成协议，这家日本公司将在安大略省生产电动汽车及其零部件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/honda-is-near-deal-with-canada-to-boost-electric-vehicle-capacity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 00:56:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
